b'[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)  \n[English](../gita/bg12.htm)  \n[Previous](bgs11.htm)  [Next](bgs13.htm)\n\n* * *\n\nXII. atha dv\xc4\x81da\xc5\x9bodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (bhaktiyoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)  \n  \narjuna uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \neva\xe1\xb9\x83 satatayukt\xc4\x81 ye bhakt\xc4\x81s tv\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 paryup\xc4\x81sate  \nye c\xc4\x81py ak\xe1\xb9\xa3aram avyakta\xe1\xb9\x83 te\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 ke yogavittam\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n12.1  \n  \n\xc5\x9br\xc4\xabbhagav\xc4\x81n uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nmayy \xc4\x81ve\xc5\x9bya mano ye m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 nityayukt\xc4\x81 up\xc4\x81sate  \n\xc5\x9braddhay\xc4\x81 parayopet\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 te me yuktatam\xc4\x81 mat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.2  \n  \nye tv ak\xe1\xb9\xa3aram anirde\xc5\x9bya\xe1\xb9\x83 avyakta\xe1\xb9\x83 paryup\xc4\x81sate  \nsarvatragam acintya\xe1\xb9\x83 ca k\xc5\xab\xe1\xb9\xadastha\xe1\xb9\x83 acala\xe1\xb9\x83 dhruvam  \n12.3  \n  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x83niyamyendriyagr\xc4\x81ma\xe1\xb9\x83 sarvatra samabuddhay\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nte pr\xc4\x81pnuvanti m\xc4\x81m eva sarvabh\xc5\xabtahite rat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.4  \n  \nkle\xc5\x9bodhikataras te\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 avyakt\xc4\x81saktacetas\xc4\x81m  \navyakt\xc4\x81 hi gatir du\xe1\xb8\xa5kha\xe1\xb9\x83 dehavadbhir av\xc4\x81pyate 12.5  \n  \nye tu sarv\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87i karm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87i mayi sa\xe1\xb9\x83nyasya matpara\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nananyenaiva yogena m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 dhy\xc4\x81yanta up\xc4\x81sate 12.6  \n  \nte\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 aha\xe1\xb9\x83 samuddhart\xc4\x81 m\xe1\xb9\x9btyusa\xe1\xb9\x83s\xc4\x81ras\xc4\x81gar\xc4\x81t  \nbhav\xc4\x81mi na cir\xc4\x81t p\xc4\x81rtha mayy \xc4\x81ve\xc5\x9bitacetas\xc4\x81m 12.7  \n  \nmayy eva mana \xc4\x81dhatsva mayi buddhi\xe1\xb9\x83 nive\xc5\x9baya  \nnivasi\xe1\xb9\xa3yasi mayy eva ata \xc5\xabrdhva\xe1\xb9\x83 na sa\xe1\xb9\x83\xc5\x9baya\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.8  \n  \natha citta\xe1\xb9\x83 sam\xc4\x81dh\xc4\x81tu\xe1\xb9\x83 na \xc5\x9bakno\xe1\xb9\xa3i mayi sthiram  \nabhy\xc4\x81sayogena tato m\xc4\x81m ich\xc4\x81ptu\xe1\xb9\x83 dhana\xe1\xb9\x83jaya 12.9  \n  \nabhy\xc4\x81sepy asamarthosi matkarmaparamo bhava  \nmadartham api karm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87i kurvan siddhim av\xc4\x81psyasi  \n12.10  \n  \nathaitad apy a\xc5\x9baktosi kartu\xe1\xb9\x83 madyogam \xc4\x81\xc5\x9brita\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsarvakarmaphalaty\xc4\x81ga\xe1\xb9\x83 tata\xe1\xb8\xa5 kuru yat\xc4\x81tmav\xc4\x81n 12.11  \n  \n\xc5\x9breyo hi j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nam abhy\xc4\x81s\xc4\x81j j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81d dhy\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb9\x83 vi\xc5\x9bi\xe1\xb9\xa3yate  \ndhy\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81t karmaphalaty\xc4\x81gas ty\xc4\x81g\xc4\x81c ch\xc4\x81ntir anantaram  \n12.12  \n  \nadve\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xad\xc4\x81 sarvabh\xc5\xabt\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 maitra\xe1\xb8\xa5 karu\xe1\xb9\x87a eva ca  \nnirmamo niraha\xe1\xb9\x83k\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb8\xa5 samadu\xe1\xb8\xa5khasukha\xe1\xb8\xa5 k\xe1\xb9\xa3am\xc4\xab  \n12.13  \n  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x83tu\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xada\xe1\xb8\xa5 satata\xe1\xb9\x83 yog\xc4\xab yat\xc4\x81tm\xc4\x81 d\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb8\x8dhani\xc5\x9bcaya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nmayy arpitamanobuddhir yo madbhakta\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa me  \npriya\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.14  \n  \nyasm\xc4\x81n nodvijate loko lok\xc4\x81n nodvijate ca ya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nhar\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81mar\xe1\xb9\xa3abhayodvegair mukto ya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa ca me priya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n12.15  \n  \nanapek\xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9bucir dak\xe1\xb9\xa3a ud\xc4\x81s\xc4\xabno gatavyatha\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsarv\xc4\x81rambhaparity\xc4\x81g\xc4\xab yo madbhakta\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa me priya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n12.16  \n  \nyo na h\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb9\xa3yati na dve\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadi na \xc5\x9bocati na k\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x85k\xe1\xb9\xa3ati  \n\xc5\x9bubh\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bubhaparity\xc4\x81g\xc4\xab bhaktim\xc4\x81n ya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa me priya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n12.17  \n  \nsama\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9batrau ca mitre ca tath\xc4\x81 m\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81pam\xc4\x81nayo\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n\xc5\x9b\xc4\xabto\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87asukhadu\xe1\xb8\xa5khe\xe1\xb9\xa3u sama\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa\xe1\xb9\x85gavivarjita\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.18  \n  \ntulyanind\xc4\x81stutir maun\xc4\xab sa\xe1\xb9\x83tu\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xado yena kenacit  \naniketa\xe1\xb8\xa5 sthiramatir bhaktim\xc4\x81n me priyo nara\xe1\xb8\xa5 12.19  \n  \nye tu dharmy\xc4\x81m\xe1\xb9\x9btam ida\xe1\xb9\x83 yathokta\xe1\xb9\x83 paryup\xc4\x81sate  \n\xc5\x9braddadh\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81 matparam\xc4\x81 bhakt\xc4\x81s tet\xc4\xabva me priy\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n12.20  \n  \n\n* * *\n\n[Next: XIII. atha trayoda\xc5\x9bodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (k\xe1\xb9\xa3etrak\xe1\xb9\xa3etraj\xc3\xb1avibh\xc4\x81gayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)](bgs13.htm)\n\n'